    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  We assessed the pharmacokinetics of favipiravir (FPV) in adults with symptomatic SARS-CoV-2 infection without pneumonia in Thailand. FPV dosing was 1800 mg twice-daily on day 1, then 800 mg twice-daily for 14 days. Eight subjects (7 female), median (range) age 39 (19-53) years and BMI 27.9 (18.0-33.6) were included. Inter-subject variability was high but all achieved minimum plasma concentrations (C\n                  <jats:sub>min</jats:sub>\n                  ) above EC\n                  <jats:sub>50</jats:sub>\n                  (9.7 mg/L). FPV was well tolerated; 1 subject stopped prematurely due to rash.\n                </jats:p>",
